with complications

204
00:08:44,504 --> 00:08:46,541
and a long recovery.

205
00:08:47,767 --> 00:08:48,759
Are you with me?

206
00:08:48,843 --> 00:08:50,001
Uh, sort of.

207
00:08:50,085 --> 00:08:53,396
Uh, you understand, right?
I'm not a doctor.

208
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,835
I'm a cartoonist.

209
00:08:55,044 --> 00:08:56,480
Right.

210
00:08:56,564 --> 00:08:58,892
