211
00:08:59,503 --> 00:09:00,849
Do you take risks?

212
00:09:00,933 --> 00:09:03,052
If you do,
then we go with the surgery.

213
00:09:03,136 --> 00:09:05,849
Are you cautious?
Then we hold off for now,

214
00:09:05,933 --> 00:09:07,698
