I need a surgery?

236
00:09:53,508 --> 00:09:55,268
Yeah, and it's just
an outpatient procedure.

237
00:09:55,352 --> 00:09:57,651
No general anesthesia,
no operating room.

238
00:09:57,735 --> 00:09:58,862
